    "complement_intervention_rate_cap": 0.25
  },
  "selection_rule": "Among candidates passing every calibration safety constraint and improving calibration failure-target q9-WQL, select the lowest failure-target q9-WQL, then the lowest complement intervention rate. If none pass, deploy Native.",
  "external_confirmation_requirement": "Freeze one selected policy before evaluation on untouched whole-domain, disjoint-series, non-overlapping-origin data. This development endpoint cannot support the final claim."
